Razorclaw slowly rises exposing himself then, the other predacons follow in 
coming foreward.  The five slowly make a semicircle around Megatron. Tantrum 
is the first to speak:

**Tantrum** "You are not Galvatron...but you almost have the same 
signature..."

The predacons uniformly transform into thier robot modes, Razorclaw stepping 
foreward.

**Razorclaw** "State your name and faction."
